title: My 10 Books - December 2015 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 diverse books for this month, 7 true PDFs & 3 ePUBS:

01. Why - A Guide to Finding and Using Causes by Samantha Kleinberg
02. Athenian Prostitution - The Business of Sex by Edward Cohen
03. Bigger Leaner Stronger - The Simple Science of Building the Ultimate Male Body, 2nd Edition
04. Chemistry - The Impure Science (2nd Ed) by Bernadette Bensaude-Vincent, Jonathan Simon
05. Essential Ornithology by Graham Scott
06. Feast of Excess - A Cultural History of the New Sensibility
07. Nobel Prizes That Changed Medicine by Thompson, G. R.
08. Sandbag Training Bible - Functional Workouts to Tone, Sculpt and Strengthen Your Entire Body
09. Team Builder Toolbox - 13 Tools To Build The Power Of Your Team
10. The Concise Routledge Encyclopedia of the Documentary Film by Ian Aitken
